name: Liability of general partner and person dissociated as general partner when claim against limited partnership barred
text: [§425E-808]  Liability of general partner and person dissociated as general partner when claim against limited partnership barred.  If a claim against a dissolved limited partnership is barred under section 425E-806 or 425E-807, any corresponding claim under section 425E-404 shall also be barred. [L 2003, c 210, pt of §1]
